  "title": "Temporal Binding Windows",
  "concept": "Events that happen close enough in time can link into a single pattern if the window capturing them is wide enough—no repetition required.",
  "interactiveId": "82a4fe4d-d131-4e6b-bb99-6794b2719b12",
  "sourcePieceId": "4151bae5-320c-437d-ad38-b2bb7d003b67",
  "publishedAt": 1777669091698,
  "voiceScore": 90,
  "qualityFlag": "low",
  "content": {
    "type": "html",
    "html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n<title>Temporal Binding Windows</title>\n<style>\n  :root {\n    --bg: #faf7f1;\n    --fg: #1a1a1a;\n    --muted: #6b6b6b;\n    --line: #e5e0d6;\n    --gold: #c9a227;\n    --teal: #1a6b62;\n    --active: #c44536;\n  }\n  * { box-sizing: border-box; }\n  body {\n    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, \"Segoe UI\", sans-serif;\n    margin: 0;\n    padding: 20px;\n    color: var(--fg);\n    background: var(--bg);\n    line-height: 1.5;\n  }\n  h2 {\n    font-size: 1.05rem;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    margin: 0 0 4px;\n  }\n  p.subhead {\n    margin: 0 0 20px;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .control {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n  }\n  .control label {\n    font-weight: 500;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .control input[type=range] {\n    flex: 1;\n    accent-color: var(--teal);\n    min-width: 140px;\n  }\n  .control output {\n    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;\n    font-weight: 600;\n    min-width: 4ch;\n    text-align: right;\n  }\n  .stream-container {\n    position: relative;\n    height: 200px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 8px;\n    margin: 24px 0 16px;\n    padding: 20px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .timeline-axis {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 30px;\n    left: 20px;\n    right: 20px;\n    height: 1px;\n    background: var(--line);\n  }\n  .key-moment {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 26px;\n    left: 50%;\n    width: 3px;\n    height: 9px;\n    background: var(--active);\n    transform: translateX(-50%);\n  }\n  .key-label {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 8px;\n    left: 50%;\n    transform: translateX(-50%);\n    font-size: 0.75rem;\n    color: var(--active);\n    font-weight: 600;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n  }\n  .window-band {\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: 24px;\n    height: 14px;\n    background: var(--teal);\n    opacity: 0.15;\n    border-radius: 7px;\n    transition: all 260ms ease-out;\n    pointer-events: none;\n  }\n  .events-layer {\n    position: absolute;\n    top: 20px;\n    left: 20px;\n    right: 20px;\n    bottom: 50px;\n  }\n  .pulse {\n    position: absolute;\n    width: 4px;\n    height: 4px;\n    background: var(--gold);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    opacity: 0.4;\n    transition: all 260ms ease-out;\n  }\n  .pulse.linked {\n    width: 6px;\n    height: 6px;\n    background: var(--teal);\n    opacity: 1;\n  }\n  .reading {\n    margin: 18px 0 6px;\n    padding: 12px 16px;\n    background: #fff;\n    border: 1px solid var(--line);\n    border-radius: 6px;\n    font-size: 0.9rem;\n  }\n  .reading strong {\n    font-weight: 600;\n  }\n  p.caption {\n    margin: 14px 0 0;\n    color: var(--muted);\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n  }\n  @media (max-width: 520px) {\n    .stream-container {\n      height: 180px;\n      padding: 16px;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<h2>Drag to widen the binding window</h2>\n<p class=\"subhead\">Pulses fire continuously. A wider window around the key moment links more of them together.</p>\n\n<div class=\"control\">\n  <label for=\"window\">Window:</label>\n  <input id=\"window\" type=\"range\" min=\"5\" max=\"80\" value=\"20\" step=\"1\" aria-describedby=\"window-out\">\n  <output id=\"window-out\" for=\"window\">20</output>%\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"stream-container\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  <div class=\"timeline-axis\"></div>\n  <div class=\"key-moment\"></div>\n  <div class=\"key-label\">Key moment</div>\n  <div class=\"window-band\" id=\"window-band\"></div>\n  <div class=\"events-layer\" id=\"events-layer\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"reading\">\n  Events linked: <strong id=\"count\">3</strong>. <span id=\"detail\">Only pulses right at the moment connect</span>.\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"caption\" id=\"caption\">A narrow window links only what happens right now. A wider window reaches back and forward, binding more events into one pattern from a single pass.</p>\n\n<script>\n(function () {\n  var slider = document.getElementById('window');\n  var windowOut = document.getElementById('window-out');\n  var windowBand = document.getElementById('window-band');\n  var eventsLayer = document.getElementById('events-layer');\n  var countEl = document.getElementById('count');\n  var detailEl = document.getElementById('detail');\n  var captionEl = document.getElementById('caption');\n\n  var keyPos = 50;\n  var pulseCount = 40;\n  var pulses = [];\n\n  function initPulses() {\n    eventsLayer.innerHTML = '';\n    pulses = [];\n    for (var i = 0; i < pulseCount; i++) {\n      var t = (i / (pulseCount - 1)) * 100;\n      var y = 10 + Math.random() * 60;\n      var el = document.createElement('div');\n      el.className = 'pulse';\n      el.style.left = t + '%';\n      el.style.top = y + '%';\n      eventsLayer.appendChild(el);\n      pulses.push({el: el, t: t});\n    }\n  }\n\n  function update() {\n    var w = +slider.value;\n    windowOut.textContent = w;\n    var halfW = w / 2;\n    var left = keyPos - halfW;\n    var right = keyPos + halfW;\n\n    windowBand.style.left = left + '%';\n    windowBand.style.right = (100 - right) + '%';\n\n    var linked = 0;\n    for (var i = 0; i < pulses.length; i++) {\n      var p = pulses[i];\n      if (p.t >= left && p.t <= right) {\n        p.el.className = 'pulse linked';\n        linked++;\n      } else {\n        p.el.className = 'pulse';\n      }\n    }\n\n    countEl.textContent = linked;\n\n    if (w <= 15) {\n      detailEl.textContent = 'Only pulses right at the moment connect';\n      captionEl.textContent = 'A narrow window links only what happens right now. Events before and after stay separate.';\n    } else if (w <= 35) {\n      detailEl.textContent = 'Pulses near the moment connect';\n      captionEl.textContent = 'A moderate window reaches a short distance before and after, linking nearby events into one pattern.';\n    } else if (w <= 60) {\n      detailEl.textContent = 'Pulses across a stretch connect';\n      captionEl.textContent = 'A wider window links events across time. Things that fired earlier or later now belong to the same pattern.';\n    } else {\n      detailEl.textContent = 'Most pulses connect';\n      captionEl.textContent = 'A very wide window binds almost everything into one pattern from a single pass—no repetition needed.';\n    }\n  }\n\n  initPulses();\n  slider.addEventListener('input', update);\n  update();\n})();\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
  }
}
